Clump of rocks is located in the lake north of the Mountain Camp. It is used in the Mountain Daughter quest to reach the island and the centre of the lake. The player must use either a pole or any staff on the clump of rocks to vault over, as attempting to jump-across will result in the player falling into the lake and swimming back to shore.

After the quest, the clump of rocks cannot be reached, because the tree leading to the first island in the lake can no longer be climbed.

'''Clump of rocks''' is located in the lake north of the [[Mountain Camp]]. It is used in the [[Mountain Daughter]] [[quest]] to reach the island and the centre of the lake. The player must use either a [[pole]] or any [[Staves|staff]] on the clump of rocks to vault over, as attempting to jump-across will result in the player falling into the lake and swimming back to shore.

After the quest, the clump of rocks cannot be reached, because the tree leading to the first island in the lake can no longer be climbed.
